name: Honor of Kings LoRA
description:
This LoRA was trained on GuoFeng3_v32Light as base model using 500 Honor of Kings character artworks (with their logo) so that mean a lot of the generated images will have the HoK logo (maybe I will manually remove those logo and retrain them in future version, so try negative Logo & see if it helps).

100-128dim-64NA-512x

100 Steps - 128 Network Rank (Dimension) - 64 Network Alpha - 512 Max resolution

HoK-100-128dim-64NA-1024x

100 Steps - 128 Network Rank (Dimension) - 64 Network Alpha - 1024 Max resolution

Note: This model don't do too well on faces and male images probably because the training images didn't solely focus on faces and male images, so the faces is kinda weird sometimes, you've been warned.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Manually adjust cropping to focus on character and trained on 768x Resolution

HoK-100Steps-128dim-64NA-768x
